      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a new owner with a vision to bring it back to its former glory. While it is currently in poor condition and will require some dedicated mechanical and cosmetic attention, it serves as a fantastic, budget-friendly foundation for a rewarding restoration project. If you're looking for an affordable way to get your hands on a car with potential, this is the one for you!",
