      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the ideal choice for a discerning buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior maintains a strong shelf presence with a deep luster in the paint, showing only the subtle signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin remains remarkably clean; the seats are supportive and free of significant wear, while all tactile controls and infotainment features operate exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, a testament to a consistent maintenance schedule. From the crisp handling to the quiet cabin environment, this car offers a refined driving experience that belies its mileage. It is a solid, honest example of the model, ready to provide years of dependable service.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
